Create react app (to bootstrap a react application) is released by facebook. 
get started with how to work with create react app :
Step1: Install the create react app package. (For this you need to have nodejs and npm installed)
-g opiton to install globally -- that means the installed binary executables will be available anywhere..

1. Install Node.js and NPM
2. Test if node and npm is installed ( Node -v, npm -v)
3. Install create-react-app (npm install -g create-react-app)
4. Your first reactapp (create-react-app myFirstReactApp) creates the react app in the specificd folder "MyFirstReactApp"
5. npm start -> to start your app.

